quran[7{c,v,t}:
62,9,momino! jab jummey ke din namaz ke liye azaan di jaye to khuda ki yaad ( yani namaz ) ke liye jaldi karo aur ( kharedo ) farokht tark kardo. agar samjhoo to yeh tumahray haq mein behtar hai
62,10,phir jab namaz ho chukay to apni apni raah lau aur khuda ka fazl talaash karo aur khuda ko bohat bohat yaad karte raho taakay nijaat pao
62,11,aur jab yeh log soda bikta ya tamasha hota dekhte hain to idhar bhaag jatay hain aur tumhe ( kharray ka ) khara chore jatay hain. keh do ke jo cheez khuda ke haan hai woh tamashay aur saudey se kahin behtar hai aur khuda sab se behtar rizaq dainay wala hai
63,1,( ae Muhammad Sallallahu Alaihiwasallam ) jab munhafiq log tumahray paas atay hain to ( az raah nifaq ) kehte hain ke hum iqraar karte hain ke aap be shak khuda ke paighambar hain aur khuda jaanta hai ke dar haqeeqat tum is ke paighambar ho lekin khuda zahir kiye deta hai ke munhafiq ( dil se aitqaad nah rakhnay ke lehaaz se ) jhutay hain
63,2,unhon ne apni qasmon ko dhaal bana rakha hai aur un ke zariye se ( logon ko ) raah khuda se rok rahay hain. kuch shak nahi ke jo kaam yeh karte hain buray hain
63,3,yeh is liye ke yeh ( pehlay to ) imaan laaye phir kafir hogaye to un ke dilon par mohar lagadi gayi. so ab yeh samajte hi nahi
63,4,aur jab tum un ( ke tanasub aaza ) ko dekhte ho to un ke jism tumhe (kiya hi ) achay maloom hotay hain. aur jab woh guftagu karte hain to tum un ki taqreer ko tavajja se suntay ho ( magar feham o adraak se khaali ) goya lakdiyaan hain jo dewaron se lagai gayi hain. ( buzdil aisay ke ) har zor ki aawaz ko samjhain ( ke ) un par bulaa aayi. yeh ( tumahray ) dushman hain un se be khauf nah rehna. khuda un ko halaak kere. yeh kahan behke phirtay hain
